OL,3,CAt least 65 dead after new Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak confirmed in DR Congo
OL,6,FAt least 65 people have died after an
OL,7,FEbola outbreak in the Democratic
OL,8,FRepublic of Congo's remote Ituri
OL,9,Fprovince, Africa's top public health
OL,10,Fbody has said.
OL,12,FAs of Friday, more than 246 suspected
OL,13,Fcases of the disease have been
OL,14,Frecorded, mainly in the Mongwalu and
OL,15,FRwampara health zones.
OL,17,FEbola is a highly contagious virus and
OL,18,Fis spread through bodily fluids such
OL,19,Fas vomit, blood, or semen. The disease
OL,20,Fit causes is rare but severe, and
OL,21,Foften fatal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
