OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778883107
OL,3,CAt least 65 dead after new Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak confirmed in DR Congo
OL,6,FThe symptoms start with flu-like signs
OL,7,Fsuch as high fever, fatigue, muscle
OL,8,Fand joint pain, headache, and sore
OL,9,Fthroat, and there is no cure.
OL,11,FThe Africa Centres for Disease Control
OL,12,Fand Prevention (CDC) said four deaths
OL,13,Fhave been reported among laboratory-
OL,14,Fconfirmed cases, while suspected cases
OL,15,Fhave also been reported in Bunia.
OL,17,FIturi is in a remote eastern part of
OL,18,FDR Congo and is more than 1,000
OL,19,Fkilometres (620 miles) from the
OL,20,Fnation's capital of Kinshasa.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
