CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1778883107
OL,3,CAt least 65 dead after new Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak confirmed in DR Congo
OL,6,FAfrica CDC said it is concerned about
OL,7,Fthe risk of further spread due to
OL,8,Fintense population movement, mining-
OL,9,Frelated mobility in Mongwalu,
OL,10,Finsecurity in affected areas, gaps in
OL,11,Fcontact listing and control challenges.
OL,13,FThe proximity of affected areas to
OL,14,FUganda and South Sudan also raises
OL,15,Fconcerns, it said.
OL,17,FThe new cases come five months after
OL,18,FDR Congo's last Ebola outbreak, which
OL,19,Fsaw 43 deaths. It marks the country's
OL,20,F17th outbreak since the disease first
OL,21,Femerged in the Congo in 1976.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
