OL,3,CAt least 65 dead after new Ebola
OL,4,Coutbreak confirmed in DR Congo
OL,6,FDR Congo's deadliest outbreak was
OL,7,Fbetween 2018 and 2020, during which
OL,8,Fnearly 2,300 people died, according to
OL,9,Fthe World Health Organization. It was
OL,10,Falso the world's second-largest Ebola
OL,11,Foutbreak on record, before it was
OL,12,Fdeclared over on June 25, 2020.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
